    "body": "The custom logger in this repo is ugly. Let's just use Pino.\n\nLocal dev should write to the console. In deployed environments let the `LOG_FORMAT=json` environment variable switch it to JSON logging.\n\nMake sure to include good custom context on each request's logger and pass that logger through the dispatcher to the appropriate handler so that it has all the context. \n\n- Request ID\n- Delivery ID\n- Event Name",
